description.2: BARON BLOOD has come! The King of Vampires has a vendetta with Doctor Strange -- but why? Secrets and stunning truths revealed!
description.3: The Punisher and Microchip are hot on the trail of Hawaiian drug dealers who attacked an innocent family vacationing on the island!
description.4: A united Scarlet Witch, Quicksilver and Magneto means big trouble for the Avengers West Coast!
description.5: What if the X-Men had stayed in Asgard? After the Asgardian Wars end, the X-Men decide to make a new realm their home. But Loki's nefarious streak might mean doom for the X-Men!
description.8: Kitty Pryde has been separated from the rest of Excalibur! And to make matters worse, the team has been stranded in an alternate reality! How will Excalibur find their way home? And who is the strangely familiar figure known only as Crusader X?
description.9: Upon being ambushed by Doc Samson and company in Las Vegas, Hulk jumps aboard a moving freight train...where he encounters a shadowy figure.
description.10: It's double trouble in this action-packed issue! Crimson Dynamo versus the Devastator! Iron Man versus who?
description.11: The Dark Dweller has struck--and he holds Hercules and the Masterson family in his thrall! How can Thor and Eric possibly fight back against their own kin?
description.15: The source of the Time Bubble is revealed - Galactus! To stop him devouring the universe, the FF must team up with Gladiator of the Shi'ar Empire! Too bad he's more interested in throwing down with the Mighty Thor!
description.16: Dazzler battles for her life...and the rights to her feature film! It's pure Hollywood drama as Dazzler is stuck between two producers, both making offers she just can't refuse!
description.19: Spider-Man and Punisher make their way to the source of the drug warfare. Meanwhile, the secret of Eddy Brock's demise is revealed...
description.20: Iron Man and Vision journey to the moon to confront Nebula's starship. Will Nebula succumb to the power of Earth's Mightiest Heroes? Plus, who is the furious stranger who greets the Avengers in space?
description.21: The Black Queen and the Hellfire Mercenaries versus Crossfire and the Skeleton Crew - and Cap and Diamondback are caught in the middle!
description.26: The Punisher risks losing it all in the concluding chapter to his undercover mission inside a drug-trading biker gang.
description.27: Conan seeks vengeance against those who have wronged him, but when another warrior out for revenge threatens to get in his way, Conan might just have to kill him first!
description.28: Who, or what, is haunting the apartment complex of the Power family? Stay tuned for the reveal of a surprising Super-Villain!
description.29: The Black Widow discovers that her husband, the Red Guardian, may be alive! But before she can see him, the Russians demand that she betray America by stealing one of its most precious secrets!
description.32: Daredevil continues the search for Black Bolt's son with the INHUMANS!
description.34: The newly revived vampires are after the Darkhold, and unleashing its power would throw the world into chaos! Can Doctor Strange stop them from escaping with the dark tome?
description.36: Spider-Man teams up with the Punisher to fight a gang of race supremacists which has captured the Daily Bugle building, and unknown to the Punisher — taken Spider-Man's wife, Mary Jane, hostage!
description.39: Meggan lets her feelings - and the Phoenix - get the best of her, and all hell breaks loose! Meanwhile, can Kitty send the Demon Druid back to his own world before it's too late? And why is Captain Britain acting so strangely?
description.40: Hulk finds the aptly-named Madman. Our hero must either face death in battle...or succumb to radiation poisoning!
description.41: After undergoing a grueling, deadly elimination competition at the Taskmaster's Academy, the survivor is named the new Spymaster. In order to graduate, Spymaster must steal the top Christmas ornament at Stark's party.
description.42: First Appearance of Cable.  Here comes the man called Cable!  With the rest of the team in Asgard, Rusty and Skids are arrested by Freedom Force. The terrorist Mutant Liberation Front demands their release, but a mysterious metal-armed, gun-toting warrior with a glowing eye is targeting the MLF for reasons of his own!
description.43: Eric Masterson has a god living within him, and with that god comes a duty to protect the Earth. But he was not the only mortal to bear this burden. Watch as Eric reflects on the life of the first human to wield mighty Mjolnir--Dr. Donald Blake!
description.47: With time travel involved, it's a sure thing that the FF would come face to face with Kang the Conqueror! But he's not their only threat, as they're also ambushed by Death's Head, bounty hunter of the 82nd century!
description.48: Colossus saves two Genoshan fugitives who have come under trouble with the law. Meanwhile, an amnesiac Dazzler pursues a movie career in Hollywood. But who really holds the strings to her future success? And what desperate measures will she take to become a bona fide star?
description.51: Spidey and Punisher find themselves in the midst of a major drug war. As gangs trade bullets over the right to distribute, a few states over Eddy Brock is found dead!
description.52: After Nebula's attempt to achieve ultimate power, only Thor, Jarvis, Sersi, and Captain America remain in the universe. Why were these heroes spared from the void? And what desperate actions will they need to take in order to restore reality?
description.53: Magneto's gone crazy- attacking a peaceful mutant demonstration in Washington. So...how's this going to lead Crossbones and Machinesmith to the Red Skull? Plus: the origin of Machinesmith!
description.54: Darker than Scarlet! What has caused Wanda to lash out against her Avengers West Coast teammates?
description.55: What if the Fantastic Four all had the same powers? Witness four fantastically told stories about the FF all receiving the powers to stretch, flame on, turn invisible or become as strong as the hardest rock!
description.57: Franklin Richards and Jack Power take on the Mad Thinker—and his ravenous dinosaurs—in a suburban mall!
description.58: She-Hulk heads out for a much-needed vacation but finds herself in the middle of a town that appears to be possessed by some malevolent being.
description.61: Frank Castle: Undercover agent? The Punisher puts on the guise of a hardcore biker to infiltrate a gang of drug traders.
description.62: Conan plays the part of a deadly emissary in a tale of fraternal malevolence, long distance assassination, and sorcerous shenanigans.
description.66: After the devastating events of last issue, Matt Murdock needs time to reflect and unwind. But what secrets does the home of his psychologist hold?
description.70: Strange reveals a dark secret of his past that will change the Marvel Universe forever! VAMPIRES stalk the night of the Marvel Universe once more!
description.71: A group of Neo-Nazis makes their way to the Daily Bugle office, where they keep the entire staff hostage!
description.73: With the help of Phoenix, Meggan is able to fight Jamie Braddock by transforming into different X-Men! Plus - can Widget save Kitty from the reality she is trapped in?!
description.74: The Leader has the cure for Hulk's deadly disease- in exchange for one small favor. Will Betty's whereabouts remain a mystery?
description.75: Stark meets old friend Joey Cosmatos, who is being harassed by thugs. When Stark tries to help him, he'll find several surprises.
description.76: Thor and Hercules battle Ulik the Troll, but can they defeat him in their weakened states? And can Thor possibly salvage the crumbling personal life of Eric Masterson?
description.77: ACTS OF VENGEANCE The Wizard, having recovered Spider-Man's mask, puts Dragon Man on Spidey's scent.
description.80: When Reed discovers that the timestream is in danger because of a mysterious Time Bubble, the Fantastic Four suit up and travel forward in time to destoy it! But they won't have to do it alone, as Iron Man and Thor join them to lend a hand!
description.81: Wolverine has been captured by The Hand, a mysterious ninja organization that works under The Mandarin. Susceptible to Psylocke's psychic powers of possession, will Wolverine be able to escape with his mind, and body, intact?
description.84: Acts of Vengeance! The villains' plan may just mean the end for the Marvel heroes, including the Avengers West Coast. Featuring the villainy of Wizard, Mandarin, Kingpin, Loki and more!
description.85: What if the Punisher's family had not been killed? The defining moment in forging the Punisher is the death of his wife and kids, gunned down by mobsters. But if that never happens, does the Punisher ever exist? Well, in this universe, it will be corruption, not tradegy, that will birth the Punisher.
description.88: Note: this issue does not collect reprinted material from UNCANNY X-MEN (1963) #138. ""Her First & Last."" Starring Rogue! Scrappy, carefree, and full of life-relive a moment from Rogue's childhood when she was still rolling with Mystique and Destiny. An adolescent kiss means a whole lot more to a girl who can absorb memories.
description.93: It’s “unholy war” when the Punisher desecrates the sanctity of the confessional!
description.94: It's the bloodthirsty conclusion to "Red Eyes!" Conan's battle against the tribe of albino cannibals is most brutal!
description.95: ACTS OF VENGEANCE AFTERMATH At last! The secret of Spidey's cosmic powers revealed! And, introducing: the Tri-Sentinel!
description.96: Nebula assumes control over a covert research project, and nearly wipes out existence. Without the help of Sersi, the Avengers will perish into the void alongside humanity.
description.97: The core alliance of super villains is destroyed when Magneto attacks the Red Skull! Wait'll you see the reason why- and the side Cap chooses to help!

0.text: The New Mutants reunite with X-Factor! But Rusty and Skids have been imprisoned by Freedom Force -- and the Mutant Liberation Front has something to do with it!

2.text: BARON BLOOD has come! The King of Vampires has a vendetta with Doctor Strange -- but why? Secrets and stunning truths revealed!

3.text: The Punisher and Microchip are hot on the trail of Hawaiian drug dealers who attacked an innocent family vacationing on the island!

6.text: Quasar faces his strangest foe yet as he finds himself in the clutches of M.O.D.A.M.!

17.text: An ancient living weapon vs. Wolverine and everybody else! The fate of a nation and perhaps the world at stake! Special appearance by Magneto!

18.text: Spider-Man -- PRISONER! Hobgoblin and Carrion have taken the web-slinger captive, and things are looking grim! Only ONE of these men will leave New York's sewers alive!

22.text: She-Hulk and Howard the Duck are forced to get along while trapped in the Baloney-verse! But what happens when Shulkie can only summon the strength of Jennifer Walters?

23.text: Uncertain of his true purpose, a nearly out of his mind Namor begins a new chapter by establishing a company with his Atlantean riches -- Oracle Incorporated is born! And Namor may have already gained corporate enemies…

24.text: Moon Knight becomes a rebel leader in an attempt to destroy Bushman! Meanwhile, Arsenal is out to kill both Bushman and Moon Knight!

25.text: An underground mutant Morlock has set their sights on Dagger!

32.text: Daredevil continues the search for Black Bolt's son with the INHUMANS!

34.text: The newly revived vampires are after the Darkhold, and unleashing its power would throw the world into chaos! Can Doctor Strange stop them from escaping with the dark tome?

36.text: Spider-Man teams up with the Punisher to fight a gang of race supremacists which has captured the Daily Bugle building, and unknown to the Punisher — taken Spider-Man's wife, Mary Jane, hostage!

37.text: THE CHAOS SERPENT PART 3 Leviathan kidnaps Lump to help control his Coven. Nick Fury must rescue Lump.

42.text: Here comes the man called Cable! This is the first appearance of one of Marvel's most enduring characters!

49.text: Tierra Verde gets its super-soldier, but not in any way that anyone expected! Spore walks the Earth, and it wants Wolverine dead!

50.text: A villain team-up for the ages! The Hobgoblin is back, and he busts Carrion out of prison for a single goal -- to kill Spider-Man!

56.text: Secret Wars II tie-in! Quasar returns to Project P.E.G.A.S.U.S. only to discover a dangerous alien creature!

58.text: She-Hulk heads out for a much-needed vacation but finds herself in the middle of a town that appears to be possessed by some malevolent being.

59.text: The final chapter! The Morituri are prisoners of the alien Ancient Ones! The secret that compelled the aliens' invasion of Earth revealed!

60.text: Moon Knight joins with deadly mercenaries to free Burunda from its dictator!

66.text: After the devastating events of last issue, Matt Murdock needs time to reflect and unwind. But what secrets does the home of his psychologist hold?

67.text: The Vulture has arrived! Can Rusty take him down?

69.text: THE CHAOS SERPENT PART 2 World War III could happen at any second; Leviathan has escaped the Vault!

70.text: Strange reveals a dark secret of his past that will change the Marvel Universe forever! VAMPIRES stalk the night of the Marvel Universe once more!

71.text: A group of Neo-Nazis makes their way to the Daily Bugle office, where they keep the entire staff hostage!

82.text: Drugged by Geist, Wolverine's living in hallucinations of World War II, once more fighting the Nazis! But he's got more enemies waiting for him when he snaps out of it! Guest-starring the Celestials!

86.text: Move over Quasar -- Spider-Man is the newest cosmically powered hero on the block!

89.text: Sometimes the good guys lose and lose big! Strikeforce: Morituri, their loss against the alien New Ones means the devastation of all mankind!

90.text: Iron Man versus two power-crazed foes -- the Wizard and Klaw!

91.text: Moon Knight versus the new Arsenal and his mercenary force!

92.text: Cloak and Dagger run afoul of the Uncanny X-Force! Will this encounter lead to conflict…or an alliance?

98.text: She-Hulk—major movie star? Jennifer Walters may get a Hollywood dream come true... if she gets to play herself in her own biopic!

99.text: After the Surfer departs Earth for his home world, the heroes of Earth along with all its inhabitants are captured by the Enslavers. The Surfer must face the Enslavers' leader to save the people of Zenn-La, Earth and countless other planets.
